    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/fa8243239d6214ee343fe78d04c765cd.poster.avif?t=1741865147\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/fa8243239d6214ee343fe78d04c765cd.webm?t=1741865147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/fa8243239d6214ee343fe78d04c765cd.mp4?t=1741865147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unravel a genre-hopping mystery about neon spaceships, alien plants, digital demigods, and the nature of reality in... Attack on Mutation Station.</strong>     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/7382b3a0544039edc0ca97543c85764d.poster.avif?t=1741865147\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/7382b3a0544039edc0ca97543c85764d.webm?t=1741865147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/7382b3a0544039edc0ca97543c85764d.mp4?t=1741865147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Premise:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an elite pilot, sent to eliminate an alien, plant-like organism that has taken over a space research station. The game starts out as a colorful and campy sci-fi space shooter, but quickly turns into more of a mystery investigation as different gameplay elements are introduced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/9b1b3867ed67ff6a489b9b71a62003af.poster.avif?t=1741865147\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/9b1b3867ed67ff6a489b9b71a62003af.webm?t=1741865147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/9b1b3867ed67ff6a489b9b71a62003af.mp4?t=1741865147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your job is to...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exterminate any mutated plants on site, in glorious shoot 'em up sections inspired by classic shooter games from the 80s and 90s.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate the space station, and uncover the truth about y̴̨̽█̷̡̃█̶͎́█̴͙͗ ̸̬̎m̵̮͐█̴̠̈́█̴̳̈́█̶̤̇█̷͔̃█̴͙͝█̵̈́͜█̸̳̒  in classic 2D point &amp; click adventure fashion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Question everything, and discover the t̶̲̍͠█̴̝͆█̸͇̋█̸̢̣̲̒̿ ̶͎̺́█̵̗͂█̴̝͒̆ṯ̴́̽█̷͉̫̔͌̿█̴͚̮̐͠e̵͕̗͘ ̶̻̦͋█̴̦̫̅̚█̸̳̦̅ ̶̖̻͗̀͠ŗ̵̀̿͝█̷͚͖̽͋̃█̵͔̤̆̎█̵͈͌̔i̷̙̘̯̐█̶͉̿̌█̸͈̭̄̄  by exploring the station in first-person perspective.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn that there is more to this mission, and to this game, than meets the eye.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/6f9082574899b48b9f59ac30343573ce.poster.avif?t=1741865147\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/6f9082574899b48b9f59ac30343573ce.webm?t=1741865147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/6f9082574899b48b9f59ac30343573ce.mp4?t=1741865147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may encounter occasional █̸̲̞͌█̸͈͈̿͗͐̿█̵͕͓̻͐█̴͓͇̮̟̊█̷̦͎̘̝̈́̿̃͠█̸̹̙̰̑́̌͝ͅ█̶̞̓̊̎̕█̸̰͚͙̋͌ but don't worry, it's all part of the █̴͙̼̞̰̭́̂█̵̛̤̥̔█̶̖͑͊̿̃█̵͔̣̉̾͝.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/63b607fabed9a4a19af941b513fd5292.poster.avif?t=1741865147\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/63b607fabed9a4a19af941b513fd5292.webm?t=1741865147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/63b607fabed9a4a19af941b513fd5292.mp4?t=1741865147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
